fr.epita.sp18.model

Class ApiResponse<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.epita.sp18.model.ApiResponse<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of replied data

    public class ApiResponse<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Define a wrapper that can cover both data and message that need to be sent to API's caller via http response body. ApiResponse's properties are:

    T model - Response's data

    String message - Message sending from server to API's caller

    boolean hasError - There is error when processing the API request

    String errorMessage - Explanation of the error

    Author:
    Philip
